column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) as objId           FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) IS NOT NULL SELECT         p.objID, p.ra, p.dec, p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field,        dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type,        g.dered_u as u, g.dered_g as g, g.dered_r as r, g.dered_i as i, g.clean,        s.z as z_spec      FROM #upload u           JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id           JOIN PhotoTag p ON p.objID = x.objID            JOIN galaxy g ON g.objID = x.objID           JOIN SpecObj s ON s.bestobjid = x.objID     ORDER BY x.up_id
